<P>
Tony Taylor's lovingly sculpted essay on Voyager's odyssey to Neptune and 
beyond was, by itself, worth the price of admission to the Aug. 6 Times. 
Scientists might take note; information poetically expressed -- even technical 
information -- is a potent, effective force. 
</P>
<P>
TROY J. HOLTER 
</P>
<P>
Helena, Mont. 
</P>
